    public class OBPImpl
extends SFImpl
implements OBP
    An implementation of the model object 'OBP'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • OA Pos ID
    • RG Length
    • Xoa Oset
    • Yoa Oset
    • Xoa Orent
    • Yoa Orent
    • Xoca Oset
    • Yoca Oset
